channel.title: NEED HELP ASAP! Compiler is not picking up updates I make!
channel.description:
Okay, well. I was making some updates on my allstar server, and was compiling frequently to see if I made any errors. I made a couple making a rules list, and fixed it. (I accidently put a few rules on the same line) Then, it still says i have the same errors. Thought I would just remove the lines, and retype them. So I removed them, and compiled again, still said I have these errors. So in short: My compiler isn't picking up any updates. It just quit randomly on me at a random time. Replacing it doesn't help. The same thing still happens.
Help would be greatly appreciated. Thank you.
